Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of Echo State Networks (ESNs), which are a type of Recurrent Neural Network (RNN), and investigates their performance in time-series prediction problems. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), and Systems and Control (cs.SY). However, given the focus on ESNs and their use as predictors, cs.NE and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories.
